{"title":"忧思录二题","authors":["杜运燮"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":9,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧思录二题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜运燮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人的祖先的祖先的祖先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从水里爬上来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才学会生篝火，编瞎话，搞小动作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥霍公共财产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但人，永远跳不出水的掌心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水，就在你血液里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时能念紧箍咒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管你能垂直升空，翻筋斗遨游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用铅管编织水帘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营造摩天楼的大森林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荧屏上万亿变化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身怀窃听、窃摄的神技"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但只要忘乎所以，忘恩负义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧箍咒就照念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越狂妄，越愚蠢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就箍得越紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就会哀号，拚命弯曲身体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成臭鱼，沙粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忧文明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在幼儿园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着阿姨合唱过："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好！谢谢！对不起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当时没有挂标语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，热闹多了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处贴“礼貌用语”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么多人只对外国人说“谢谢”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对祖国同胞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却开不了口，或者学不会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者不愿讲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经以为，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会了，就算是长大成人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有中国人都会说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有小朋友还不会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今才知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有好多亿大朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要从头学起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者复习再复习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要学习好多年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比幼儿园长得多。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}